Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • verify.PolicyVerifier
      • impact_analysis.PolicyGenerator
        • tree.Node
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImpactAnalyzer

    public class Node
extends PolicyGenerator
    Represents a node in the attack graph, including its name, the type of node it is (privilege, exploit or leaf node), the list of parents, and children of that node in the graph.
    Author:
    Swapnanjan Chatterjee, schatt@iastate.edu
